EN: They treat the people of other countries like beasts.

ZH: 这个禽兽的行为触碰到了我的底线，我必须采取行动。
EN: The actions of this beast have crossed my bottom line, I must take action.

ZH: 这个男人是怎么变成禽兽的？以前他可不是这样的人。
EN: How did this man turn into a beast? He wasn't like this before.

