EN: These beasts should receive the harshest punishment to serve as a warning to society.

ZH: 这个世界上到底有多少禽兽？不断让人失望。
EN: How many beasts are there in this world? They keep disappointing people.

ZH: 这个被害人曾经被人类视为禽兽，现在他却变成了真正的禽兽。
EN: The victim once was considered a beast by humans, now he has turned into a true beast.

ZH: 这些禽兽毫无怜悯之心，完全不顾他人的感受。
